WEBVTT

00:02:58.272 --> 00:03:02.608
The more the people, the more the stories,
the more the genre of stories.

00:03:02.608 --> 00:03:08.273
From these stories, we felt
like our lives are bound to our sarees.

00:03:08.273 --> 00:03:12.444
Our brilliance, our ups
and downs are all tied to the saree.

00:03:12.444 --> 00:03:16.911
And then we started building
a bond with each other’s stories.

00:03:16.911 --> 00:03:19.166
I was often asked,

00:03:19.166 --> 00:03:21.388
“Sarees are old fashioned 


00:03:21.585 --> 00:03:22.732
and you are a modern woman.

00:03:22.732 --> 00:03:26.577
So why push people
into a time that is over?”

00:03:27.587 --> 00:03:29.376
Women write to me

00:03:29.376 --> 00:03:32.142
and tell me that after joining
the 100 Saree Pact